pi-cua-integration

This package targets the pi coding agent extension API by Mario Zechner
(@mariozechner/pi-coding-agent, distributed as @code-yeongyu/senpi) and bridges
it to Cua (https://github.com/trycua/cua, MIT licensed) for computer-use
sandboxes and host control.

